    <thetext>(In reply to Honggang LI from comment #1)
&gt; Hi, Dave
&gt;  Do you have the hardware to test openmpi over s390x?

No, but I don&apos;t have the other hardware I need to support for packages.
Why would s390 be special?

The package builds and runs %check in s390x koji with the appropriate changes
to exclude infiniband, libfabric, papi, and valgrind support.</thetext>
